Name: Stripper Anya™ 2 X-MiGuFighters
About the game: X-MiGu Fighters is the follow up to 2017's Stripper Anya: Demon Slayer! (click read more for full discription and features) IMPORTANT! If you buy this game and play on a Windows 10 System, READ THIS FIRST: / ... if you blow this off the game will not run correctly. :D Thanks! NEW & OUT NOW from X-MiGuplay: BARE BOOB BRAWLERZ: POWER CLAW / Coming soon from X-MiGuPLAY! / / X-MiGu Fighters takes us back to the world of Stripper Anya! 5 years have passed since Anya's clash with Demoniqa.What was once a group of high profile Strippers working for the Triple T is now a group of fierce fighters engaging in the RenMiGu Tournaments. Our top heavy hero Anya competes in the company of her co-dancers Ghost, Lynchu and Esstraya as well as others from new and old alien worlds. They're joined by Magnus, the Guild member that was instrumental in connecting Earth with life from beyond. Take part in each of the 14 character's individual journeys and play through the cohesive story told over 6 seasons of fighting! X-MiGu Fighters Options Include: -Tutorial -Story Mode -1 Player vs CPU Free Play Mode -2 Player vs Mode -3 Difficulty Settings -Max Rounds Options: 3, 5, or 7 -Graphics Settings Low or High -Customized Game Pad Controls X-MiGu Fighters marks X-MiGuPLAY's 2nd PC title which honors the late 90's/2000's arcade fighting game craze. This is a retro inspired 1 on 1 fighting game meant to be played lightheartedly with a comedic approach. Your friends will judge you but we won't! ;) #guiltypleasures *figures based on online data accessible to X-MiGuPLAY as of 09.25.2019
